>\n然後又再做番舊時代啲官所做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c051019436106f7a66015b8d1ff8e10ec962aac8","tid":984338,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T17:04:30.000Z","msg":"要改變就要破壞 殺滅 可惜你唔敢 因為你由細到大都被強權教育做馴民，你既暴力被弱化被壓抑，想改變，首先要擺脫所謂既教育"},{"pid":"57dfc61cd9e63270a648d980e8440f0045fc053d","tid":984338,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"17527ff682965420bfa7c0a24508f991e4dc9329","tid":984338,"uid":120772,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:55:36.000Z","msg":"如果一個人真係咁諗 咁佢既失敗就真係整定喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"呢個世界所有嘢都係整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75b287afc4258e125683d62380e8e0558f9c05c","tid":984338,"uid":81190,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"575e0b30a46051c01d7bba2202bdaa23ae47592b","tid":984338,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"你都話好難後天改，即係唔係整定啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T17:22:24.000Z","msg":"命數已定<br />\n屋企樓下報紙檔呀姐個孫，由細望到佢大<br />\n中一入咗間幾好嘅Band 1<br />\n點知突然有腦炎，死唔去<br />\n但佢講嘢已經語無倫次，思維紊亂<br />\n聽講出去番過幾份part time都做唔長<br />\n而家唯有喺報紙檔度表面上叫幫手執吓嘢<br />\n但實際坐咗喺檔口度，目光空洞咁揭啲報紙雜誌，有時仲無啦啦笑<br />\n外人唔知嘅當然會覺得怪，但同個呀姐熟絡嘅會覺得好可憐"},{"pid":"a267769251ea1066873daf11ee792f07636f14da","tid":984338,"uid":81190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b734f67aeccbffe3d89604fdda52b1e0a7c6c3","tid":984338,"uid":36297,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"世上總要有你D咁既廢人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"你入到HKU都係整定"},{"pid":"d5eeb2a322961267d2cc79ab4cda8a4a5e63915f","tid":984338,"uid":213269,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/13NYoCM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i